----------------------------------------
GHC 8.0.1 Android cross-compiler for ARM
----------------------------------------

Congratulations! You are the proud owner of a GHC ARM cross compilation
environment.

User
----

This build environment is built under the user 'androidbuilder' in the
the home directory /home/androidbuilder

user: androidbuilder
password: adb

Installed compilers
-------------------

There are two versions of the compiler installed.

1. One that targets the host architecture (x86_64)

   ~/.ghc/android-host

2. One that targets the Android platform

  ~/.ghc/$NDK_PLATFORM/$NDK_TOOLCHAIN


Environment variables
---------------------

The PATH has been extended with the path to the cross-compiler.
To access the host compiler use the prefix $GHC_HOST/bin. e.g.

  $ $GHC_HOST/bin/ghc --version

